  "text": "The clonogenic potential of the MSCs was further tested in a sphere formation assay [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . MSCs at passage 1 were seeded at 2 × 10 5 /cm 2 on an ultra-low attachment dish (Corning) in α-MEM supplemented with 10% (vol/vol) FBS. Primary cell spheres were counted after 3 days in culture, trypsinized, and re-plated. Secondary spheres were counted on day 6.",
